  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 1 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  mandatory: 1
  lines:
  - ALERT TO ALL CITIZENS
  - Just now, we have confirmed the existence of an otherworldly presence enveloping
    the surroundings of the dome.
  - "We are yet to understand it\u2019s full capabilities, but have identified that
    individuals exposed to it may be afflicted with a virus, the only currently known
    complication of which is a rash on either arm."
  - To protect citizens whilst we mitigate this problem, an evacuation is in progress
    that will be handled over the course of the following days. Information regarding
    this can be found on your computer messages.
  - Measures are also in place to prevent external forces and governing figures from
    interfering with or making use of this situation.
  - To fulfil the evacuation, all citizens are instructed to not leave their home
    without proper authorization, and to contact us if they believe they may be infected.
  - I REPEAT, CITIZENS MAY NOT LEAVE THEIR HOME WITHOUT PROPER AUTHORIZATION.
